import "../src/sass/app.scss"
import { BrowserRouter, Routes, Route } from "react-router-dom"
import Auth from "./components/login/Auth"

function app() {
  return (
    <BrowserRouter>
      <Routes>
        <Route path="/Auth" element={<Auth />} />
        <Route path="/">
        </Route>
      </Routes>
    </BrowserRouter>
  )
}

export default app
